{
  "texts": [
    "After clicking \"generate\" an image is generated and replaces the previous \"Final Prompt\".",
    "Amy can click on the flipping button to \"flip\" between the generated output and the textual prompt input like a card (Fig. 2.f).",
    "The generated image has the overall looks and stylings of the original living room, but with an added orange couch.",
    "She finds the result inspiring so she drags this image onto her moodboard canvas.",
    "A bit later, Amy is interested in alternative decoration for the living room."
  ]
}